<!--
  Boatmate — Dealer Warranty Intake Form (Dealer-only)
  ====================================================
  PURPOSE
  - Collects a dealer-submitted warranty claim for Boatmate trailers.
  - Posts multipart/form-data to a Cloudflare Worker endpoint.
  - Supports multiple file uploads (up to 10 files, 10MB each).

  IMPORTANT BUSINESS RULES (CURRENT)
  - Dealer-only form: claim_submitted_by is always "dealer" (hidden field).
  - Customer Information: FIRST/LAST name only (no customer address/phone/email).
  - Ship To: REMOVED entirely. Do not collect, validate, or send to the backend.
  - Labor rate: NOT part of this project. Do not collect or send.

  INTEGRATION ASSUMPTIONS
  - The Worker returns JSON: { ok: true, claimNumber: <number>, ... } on success
  - On failure it returns JSON: { ok: false, errors: [...] } (or message)

  MAINTENANCE NOTES
  - Keep input `name` attributes aligned with the Worker’s form-data parsing.
  - Keep IDs aligned with the front-end validation list.
  - Honeypot field name is "website" (hidden). The Worker should accept it.

  FILE: dealer-warranty-intake.html
-->

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Dealer Warranty Intake</title>

